00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,520
 and last name.

236
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,360
 What does that do?

237
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,200
 It makes you stand up straight

238
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,560
 and listen to whatever she's gonna say.

239
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,200
 It calls you to attention

240
