 because whatever she's about to say is serious.

241
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,760
 Paul is saying the exact same thing.

242
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:23,960
 He's demanding the same sort of response from Timothy.

243
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:27,280
 He tells him, "Hey, before God, I charge you."

244
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,120
 What?

245
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:29,520
 What's he charging?

246
00:09:29,580 --> 00:09:34,580
 To not quarrel about words.

247
00:09:34,580 --> 00:09:35,960
 In the Greek, that idea,

248
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:40,400
 it literally means to not engage in word wars.

249
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,380
 Like don't pick a fight with other people

